ygData.messageBody:
If you have Luclin maybe try Echo Caverns. I hear Fungusgrove is also for
that level range. But avoid the weird plant things on the wall. they cannot
be attacked or killed but they can kill you. Oh, and the giant shroom in
echo apparently undercons so don't fight it.
luv,
-Su
